  <Description>
    <Language>en</Language>
    <Type>General</Type>
    <Text>Complimentary Shuttle van service make access to Chong Nonsi BTS Station, the MRT Subway and shopping hubs of Bangkok a short but pleasant journey away.</Text>
  </Description>
  <Description>
    <Language>en</Language>
    <Type>SurroundingArea</Type>
    <Text>The hotel is strategically situated within Bangkok?s central business district of Sathon road. Only 40 minutes from Suvarnabhumi International Airport and just a short walk from the new BRT express bus line with connections to the BTS SkyTrain and MRT subway.</Text>
  </Description>
  <Description>
    <Language>en</Language>
    <Type>RoomTypes</Type>
    <Text>Modern contemporary in their design, One Bedroom suite and Two Bedrooms suite, ranging from 45 to 140 square meters, with balconies and bay windows that provide panoramic views of the cityscape and the haven of manicured gardens that surround the expansive free form swimming pool.</Text>
  </Description>
  <Description>
    <Language>en</Language>
    <Type>PropertyInformation</Type>
    <Text>Modern contemporary in their design as Service Apartment.</Text>
  </Description>
  <Description>
    <Language>en</Language>
    <Type>DiningFacilities</Type>
    <Text>All day dining restaurant offers a wonderful mix of Thai, Western and Japanese cuisine both a la carte and buffet style. Begin with a sumptuous breakfast buffet where your choice is "Remarkably Endless". Buffet dinner available on Wednesday night.  Japanese restaurant and Sushi Bar welcomes to enjoy "remarkably authentic" Japanese cuisine that is prepared only upon ordering. From Sushi and Sashimi to Noodles and Seafood specialties incorporating only the freshest of ingredients, served at our Sushi Bar or at the table.</Text>
  </Description>
  <Description>
    <Language>en</Language>
    <Type>Short</Type>
    <Text>The Lobby is medium side, it will be big enough for a group of appreox.25 pax.(with their luggage) to check in (standing in the lobby) simultaneously.</Text>
